{{en-verb|forbids|forbidding|forbid|past2=forbade|past3=forbad|forbidden}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[disallow]]; to [[proscribe]].
#: {{ux|en|Smoking in the restaurant is '''forbidden'''.}}
